    • makeRawIfNeeded

      protected Type makeRawIfNeeded​(Type type)
      This method takes a type, and, if that type is a class with type parameters, then make it a raw class. Also, if the type is a class with no type variables, but is an inner class of a raw class, then the class should be a raw class (i.e., the erasure of the type).
